-- MOVES-Macquarie Capital hires Larry Handen as a senior MD
-- 
-- Mon Oct 06, 2014 01:31PM EDT
-- None



Oct 6 (Reuters) - Macquarie Capital, the investment and capital markets unit of Macquarie Group <MQG.AX>, appointed Larry Handen as a senior managing director in its U.S. Principal Transactions Group.

Handen, who has over 25 years of experience, joins from Insight Venture Partners, where he was managing director.He has also worked at UBS Capital and PricewaterhouseCoopers Consulting.